headline: Agilent to Announce Third-Quarter Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Results on Aug. 27
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., July 17, 2025--Following an announcement earlier this week, Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) confirms it will release financial results for the third quarter of fiscal year 2025 after the stock market closes on Wednesday, Aug. 27. In addition, the company will host a conference call to discuss the results at 1:30 p.m. PDT on the same day.

headline: Agilent CFO Bob McMahon resigns
summary: Rodney Gonsalves, corporate controller and principal accounting officer, will take on interim CFO duties. Analysts said the company’s reaffirmed third-quarter guidance should reassure investors.
